up with problems

269
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:12,800
they didn't even know they had.

270
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:17,380
Somehow they just got used to
a huge bottleneck of ponies

271
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:18,940
