00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:40,000
After all the work we
just did on the farm,

333
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:43,100
I am ready for some
serious relaxation.

334
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:46,720
Thanks for letting me
know there was an opening.

